> npm init -y //Creates a package.json
> npm install express mongoose bcrypt --save //creates node_modules Files
> Create index.js file //Starting point for the node application
> node index.js // to start node script


> Create database Folder // this folder contains database Schema(Tables)
> Create file users.js inside database folder //This contains data base schema


